Plans after 0.2.0
=================

  - Find, find and replace
      o Regular expressions
          * Support all Python regular expression flags
      o Simple string search
          * Match case
          * Match entire word only
      o Target
          * Selection / current project / all open projects
          * Main text, translation text
      o Bar (gtk.Box) or dialog?
      o gtk.CellRenderer.start_editing(...) and gtk.Editable.select_region(...)
        on match


